OL,7,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,8,Fat two hospitals in the Midlands after
OL,9,F"severe and sustained pressure" on
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FStaff at Royal Stoke University
OL,13,FHospital and County Hospital in
OL,14,FStafford say there has been high
OL,15,Fdemand over the past week, with even
OL,16,Fhigher levels over the weekend.
OL,18,FPatients are being warned of long
OL,19,Fdelays and are urged to only visit A&E
OL,20,Fin a life-threatening emergency.
