OL,7,FKaty Thorpe, UHNM Chief Operating
OL,8,FOfficer said: "We have taken the
OL,9,Fdifficult decision to declare a
OL,10,Fcritical incident. This helps us to
OL,11,Ftake additional measures to maintain
OL,12,Fsafe services for our patients and
OL,13,Fthose in the community waiting for an
OL,14,Fambulance.
