OL,7,F"Locally we are working with our NHS
OL,8,Fand local authority partners to ensure
OL,9,Fthat people who need hospital and
OL,10,Femergency care can get treatment
OL,11,Fquickly and to identify any additional
OL,12,Fsupport that allows us to discharge
OL,13,Fpatients who do not require acute
OL,14,Fhospital care.
OL,16,F"As anticipated, the pressure is
OL,17,Fgreatest in our emergency departments,
OL,18,Fwhich are facing continued challenges
OL,19,Fas patients cannot be admitted to bed
OL,20,Fpromptly."
