OL,7,F"Much longer delays"
OL,9,FDr Diane Adamson, UHNM Chief Medical
OL,10,FOfficer, said: "During this time the
OL,11,Femergency departments will continue to
OL,12,Fsee the sickest patients first, which
OL,13,Fmeans, for some patients, there maybe
OL,14,Fmuch longer delays than usual.
