OL,7,F"We continue to ask the public to help
OL,8,Fus by only using A&E in a serious or
OL,9,Flife-threatening emergency. When we're
OL,10,Fdischarging patients, we ask that
OL,11,Ftheir friends or loved ones pick them
OL,12,Fup from hospital as soon as possible
OL,13,Fand have everything they need at home.
OL,15,F"I would like to thank our staff for
OL,16,Ftheir ongoing efforts during this
OL,17,Fextremely challenging period and the
OL,18,Fpublic for their understanding and co-
OL,19,Foperation."
